      <h1 class='title'>Hutton Inquiry</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='lords-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HL Deb 06 May 2004 vol 660 c70WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_70ws' title='Col. 70WS &mdash; HL Deb 06 May 2004 vol 660 c70WS' name='column_70ws' href='#column_70ws' rel='bookmark'>70WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0660P0-05722'>
        <a name='S5LV0660P0_20040506_LWS_6'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-filkin' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040506_LWS_6' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Filkin' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-filkin" title="Mr David Filkin">The Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State, Department for Constitutional Affairs (Lord Filkin)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S5LV0660P0-05722">The estimated cost to the Government of the Hutton inquiry is &#x00A3;2.54 million, of which &#x00A3;1.68 million was incurred by the actual inquiry itself.</p>
        </blockquote>
